{"id":"artificer","term":"Artificer","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>A person engaged in any kind of manual occupation (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Genesis 4:22\">Gen. 4:22</a>; <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Isaiah 3:3\">Isa. 3:3</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Genesis 4:22","Isaiah 3:3"]}